---
source: crates/astro-up-cli/tests/cli_show.rs
expression: stdout
---
Show software status

Usage: astro-up show [OPTIONS] [PACKAGE]
       astro-up show <COMMAND>

Commands:
  all        Show all catalog packages (default)
  installed  Show only installed packages
  outdated   Show packages with available updates
  backups    Show backups
  help       Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Arguments:
  [PACKAGE]  Show details for a specific package

Options:
      --json             Output format: JSON for scripting
  -v, --verbose          Increase verbosity (show debug output)
  -q, --quiet            Suppress non-error output
      --config <CONFIG>  Path to config file
  -h, --help             Print help
